<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="row-n">row <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /rəʊ/    美 /roʊ/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(一) 排；(一) 行：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>sit in the front row 
坐在前排</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He said thanks and smiled <strong>a row of</strong> perfect teeth. 
他笑着道谢，露出一排整齐美观的牙齿。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="in-a-row">in a row</h3>
<p>1.<strong>排成一排；连续地：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The children were asked to stand in a row. 
孩子们被要求站成一列。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I’ve beaten the record three times in a row. 
我已经连续三次打破这一记录了。</p></div></div>